msgstr ""

#: ../../organizer/difficult/burnout.rst:92
msgid ""
"`context is church volunteering but similar principles "
"<http://www.behindthemixer.com/how-deal-burnout-steps-i-take/>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../organizer/difficult/burnout.rst:93
msgid ""
"`general <http://money.howstuffworks.com/economics/volunteer/information"
"/volunteer-burnout2.htm>`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../organizer/difficult/burnout.rst:94
msgid ""
"`non-profit/activist <http://www.toolsforchange.net/2012/01/14/cheyennas-"
