"apologizes and agrees to have no further contact with you\" is brief. \"X"
" is very sorry that their attempts to woo you were not received in the "
"manner that was intended and will try to do better next time, they're "
"really really sorry and hope that you can find it in your heart to "
"forgive them\" is emphatically not.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../organizer/difficult/responding.rst:182
